										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p data-track="1">立秋一过，花花再逛超市的时候就发现水果已经开始悄悄地更新换代了。夏季的水果不是在大甩卖就是已经卖完了，一些秋季的时令水果开始上市了。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-723" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/0d991d8f2d14daf3d7a60fe6e48b0fd6-1024x767.png" width="1024" height="767" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/0d991d8f2d14daf3d7a60fe6e48b0fd6-1024x767.png 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/0d991d8f2d14daf3d7a60fe6e48b0fd6-300x225.png 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/0d991d8f2d14daf3d7a60fe6e48b0fd6-768x575.png 768w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/0d991d8f2d14daf3d7a60fe6e48b0fd6.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="2">立秋是二十四节气的第13个节气，立秋一到，就代表这一年真真正正的是过去了一半。但花花觉得天气还是很热，大家的生活也都没有变化。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-724" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/cf7db0d32f0aa1fd110177ef8a96a604-767x1024.png" width="767" height="1024" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/cf7db0d32f0aa1fd110177ef8a96a604-767x1024.png 767w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/cf7db0d32f0aa1fd110177ef8a96a604-225x300.png 225w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/cf7db0d32f0aa1fd110177ef8a96a604-768x1025.png 768w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/cf7db0d32f0aa1fd110177ef8a96a604.png 959w" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, 767px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="3">但随着年龄的增长，花花的身体竟然成了最先感觉到立秋来了的，嘴里已经起了一个溃疡。有7种常见的水果，秋天吃正是好时候，对降温败火都有一定的效果，健康又促进肠道消化。秋天的时令水果有哪些？</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-725" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/0581e677862be7961b7a778110d6ca01.png" width="596" height="675" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/0581e677862be7961b7a778110d6ca01.png 596w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/0581e677862be7961b7a778110d6ca01-265x300.png 265w" sizes="(max-width: 596px) 100vw, 596px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="4"><strong>一、柚子</strong></p>
<p data-track="5">柚子是立秋最具有代表性的水果啦，柚子的维生素含量非常高，多吃柚子不光能补充维生素，它的酸还能促进肠道的消化，很适合在饭后吃。柚子皮虽然很苦，但泡成茶喝能起到很好的降火的作用，可以说立秋以后的柚子浑身都是宝。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-726" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/44d2e44b23fd3666d7db302ce7177f80-768x1024.png" width="768" height="1024" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/44d2e44b23fd3666d7db302ce7177f80-768x1024.png 768w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/44d2e44b23fd3666d7db302ce7177f80-225x300.png 225w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/44d2e44b23fd3666d7db302ce7177f80.png 960w" sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="6"><strong>二、梨</strong></p>
<p data-track="7">梨的功效想必花花也不多做介绍了，谁没有在嗓子发炎咳个不停的时候喝过几天的梨浆呢，许多止咳化痰的药物都含有梨的成分，吃起来也不苦。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-727" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/2030077bc3c16a099bc0fcd4bef22d7a.png" width="587" height="658" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/2030077bc3c16a099bc0fcd4bef22d7a.png 587w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/2030077bc3c16a099bc0fcd4bef22d7a-268x300.png 268w" sizes="(max-width: 587px) 100vw, 587px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="8">虽然花花最喜欢鲜吃梨，梨可以在平时干燥的秋季起到降噪的作用，一旦觉得身体不适了，做成汤或者冰糖雪梨喝下去，对身体的益处更大。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-728" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/f8d2f7161fc2f71500a04ef6c9f398a9-1024x768.png" width="1024" height="768" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/f8d2f7161fc2f71500a04ef6c9f398a9-1024x768.png 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/f8d2f7161fc2f71500a04ef6c9f398a9-300x225.png 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/f8d2f7161fc2f71500a04ef6c9f398a9-768x576.png 768w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/f8d2f7161fc2f71500a04ef6c9f398a9.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="9"><strong>三、柿子</strong></p>
<p data-track="10">花花的妈妈很喜欢吃甜食，柿子的口味非常甜，在其他吃不到新鲜柿子的季节，妈妈也会经常买柿子饼回来吃。但是吃柿子一定要控制量，并且也有很多需要注意的地方。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-729" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/4f8c8c9ec5d3b76927a5571568fe325e-1024x1024.png" width="1024" height="1024" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/4f8c8c9ec5d3b76927a5571568fe325e-1024x1024.png 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/4f8c8c9ec5d3b76927a5571568fe325e-300x300.png 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/4f8c8c9ec5d3b76927a5571568fe325e-150x150.png 150w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/4f8c8c9ec5d3b76927a5571568fe325e-768x768.png 768w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/4f8c8c9ec5d3b76927a5571568fe325e.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="11">柿子不能空腹吃，空腹时我们胃里的胃酸很多，而柿子里面的果胶会不容易和胃酸融合，相信不少朋友也在新闻中看到过空腹吃大量的柿子最后去了医院的新闻，轻则呕吐，重则有结石的出现。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-730" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/0414e0fab08ce759b91d2bfa97d68f6a.png" width="594" height="683" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/0414e0fab08ce759b91d2bfa97d68f6a.png 594w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/0414e0fab08ce759b91d2bfa97d68f6a-261x300.png 261w" sizes="(max-width: 594px) 100vw, 594px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="12">还有一个月以后的中秋，大闸蟹和柿子充斥着市场的节气，但这两个可不能一起食用，它们都是寒性大的食物，一起吃对胃的损伤非常大。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-731" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/5f3257d61bcfde8637fb7c999e107ca5-767x1024.png" width="767" height="1024" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/5f3257d61bcfde8637fb7c999e107ca5-767x1024.png 767w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/5f3257d61bcfde8637fb7c999e107ca5-225x300.png 225w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/5f3257d61bcfde8637fb7c999e107ca5-768x1025.png 768w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/5f3257d61bcfde8637fb7c999e107ca5.png 959w" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, 767px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="13"><strong>四、香蕉</strong></p>
<p data-track="14">香蕉对于花花来说是秋天必备水果了，饭后消食来一根香蕉，肠胃都感觉不会变得沉沉的，虽然在中医里也说香蕉有清热和止烦的功效，但花花觉得吃到甘甜的香蕉就已经是一件止烦的事情了。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-732" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/7d9fce5b5a5c7782056146cb11ffccf2.png" width="591" height="624" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/7d9fce5b5a5c7782056146cb11ffccf2.png 591w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/7d9fce5b5a5c7782056146cb11ffccf2-284x300.png 284w" sizes="(max-width: 591px) 100vw, 591px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="15"><strong>五、葡萄</strong></p>
<p data-track="16">葡萄的糖分非常高，吃多了花花都会觉得齁嗓子，但每天吃几颗对身体的新陈代谢能起到很大的作用，在低血糖的时候吃几颗葡萄能马上“回血”，补充糖分。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-733" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/292769322be1736a9f499cbb15f24565-1024x512.png" width="1024" height="512" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/292769322be1736a9f499cbb15f24565-1024x512.png 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/292769322be1736a9f499cbb15f24565-300x150.png 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/292769322be1736a9f499cbb15f24565-768x384.png 768w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/292769322be1736a9f499cbb15f24565.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="17">只是葡萄在清洗时比较麻烦，所以花花一般会在家里人多的时候一次洗很多，洗完了以后最好当天就吃完，要不然就会烂得很快啦。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-734" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/c5606c7767735ed00fba46bc6707a45d-768x1024.png" width="768" height="1024" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/c5606c7767735ed00fba46bc6707a45d-768x1024.png 768w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/c5606c7767735ed00fba46bc6707a45d-225x300.png 225w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/c5606c7767735ed00fba46bc6707a45d.png 960w" sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="18"><strong>六、石榴</strong></p>
<p data-track="19">石榴是解渴的利器之一，石榴的甜不会让人吃多了就会顶得受不了，所以非常适合做成汁喝，冰镇的石榴汁还能起到很好的降温作用。许多养花人士的家里也喜欢养一株石榴盆景，不仅非常好看，结出的果实红红火火，也有好的寓意。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-735" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/8f338f03026e64d233d31cbca3768aa4-1024x606.png" width="1024" height="606" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/8f338f03026e64d233d31cbca3768aa4-1024x606.png 1024w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/8f338f03026e64d233d31cbca3768aa4-300x178.png 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/8f338f03026e64d233d31cbca3768aa4-768x454.png 768w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/8f338f03026e64d233d31cbca3768aa4.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="20"><strong>七、杨桃</strong></p>
<p data-track="21">杨桃虽然可以做成汁，但带皮一起先吃的营养价值最高，立秋以后如果有嗓子上的不舒服，吃一两个杨桃就能缓解不适。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-736" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/d542fb7c51d6c8db832ceef7074602c7-768x1024.png" width="768" height="1024" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/d542fb7c51d6c8db832ceef7074602c7-768x1024.png 768w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/d542fb7c51d6c8db832ceef7074602c7-225x300.png 225w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/d542fb7c51d6c8db832ceef7074602c7.png 960w" sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="22">立秋吃这7种常见水果，不管是对于降温还是败火都特别有效果，秋天吃正是好时候。朋友们还喜欢吃立秋后的哪些水果呢？</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
